  • Constructor Details

    • User

      public User(String nickname, String password, String name, String surname, String emailadress, Path path, String hobbies, boolean isPremium, int age)
      This constructor takes nickname,password,name,surname,email address,path of profile photo,hobbies,information of user's subscription types and age. This method execute after register button pressed. So the registrations during execution are handled by this constructor.
      Parameters:
      nickname - - nickname of the user
      password - -password of the user which is String.
      name - - name of the user
      surname - - surname of the user
      emailadress - - email of the user
      path - - path of the profile photo
      hobbies - - hobbies of the user as a String
      isPremium - - the indicator for subscription type
      age - - age of the user

    • User

      public User(String nickname, String password, String name, String surname, String emailadress, String image, String hobbies, boolean isPremium, int age)
      This constructor is used to create all user before execution. The difference between other constructor this overloaded constructor takes image as String not Path.
      Parameters:
      nickname - - nickname of the user
      password - -password of the user which is String.
      name - - name of the user
      surname - - surname of the user
      emailadress - - email of the user
      path - - path of the profile photo
      hobbies - - hobbies of the user as a String
      isPremium - - the indicator for subscription type
      age - - age of the user

      public static User findUser(String password, String nickname)
      This method is used to check password and nickname whether they are entered correct or not.
      Parameters:

      nickname - - entered nickname in login page
      Returns:
      User or null is returned after this method. The returned User used to hold information of logined user.

      public void follow(User targetUser)
      This method is used for following operation. It takes targetUser as argument and it puts targetUser name and object to the current user following list.Also it puts current user to the follower list of target user.
      Parameters:
      targetuser - is User who is wanted to follow.
